@startuml
title Sequence - SD-006: Su dung chatbot tu van du lich

skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  DatabaseBorderColor Black
  DatabaseBackgroundColor White
}

actor "Nguoi dung" as User
boundary "Chatbot Widget" as UI
control "Chatbot API\n/api/chatbot" as API
control "DeepSeek API" as AI
database "Co so du lieu\nKnowledge Base" as DB

autonumber 1

User -> UI: Mo chatbot widget
User -> UI: Nhap cau hoi hoac chon goi y nhanh
UI -> UI: Hien thi tin nhan nguoi dung\nva trang thai dang nhap
UI -> API: POST message + sessionId\n+ token neu dang nhap

API -> API: Validate message\nLay userId, tao sessionId neu chua co
API -> DB: Luu tin nhan nguoi dung
DB --> API: Xac nhan

API -> DB: Lay context Knowledge Base\ndia diem, tour, bai viet, danh muc
DB --> API: Tra ve database context

API -> API: Tao system prompt\nkem context du lich
API -> AI: Gui system prompt + cau hoi nguoi dung
AI -> AI: Phan tich ngu nghia cau hoi\nva tong hop cau tra loi
AI --> API: Tra ve noi dung phan hoi

API -> API: Tach marker [card:slug]\nva tim dia diem duoc nhac toi
API -> DB: Query card dia diem lien quan
DB --> API: Tra ve danh sach card

API -> DB: Luu tin nhan assistant\nkem metadata model/error
DB --> API: Xac nhan

API --> UI: Tra ve reply + sessionId + cards
UI -> UI: Hien thi phan hoi\nva card dia diem neu co
UI --> User: Xem cau tra loi tu van

@enduml
